==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pothook
<hw>Pot"hook`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
<universbold>S</universbold>-shaped hook on which pots and kettles are
hung over an open fire.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A written character curved like a pothook;
(<pluf>pl.</pluf>) a scrawled writing.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧I long to be
spelling her Arabic scrawls and <xex>pothooks</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pothouse</ent>⟦br⟧
